branchCategory.description:
&lt;p&gt;
The series MSUB compact rotary table is perfect for end-of-arm tooling applications. It incorporates load bearings and a mounting face with a vane style rotary actuator. Rotation indicators on the side of the table facilitate easy rotating range adjustments.
&lt;/p&gt;

